    "However, the difference in the use of sources suggests that a combination of traditional methods and new technologies is essential to achieve an optimal balance in academic research.The results showed that the experimental group using ChatGPT outperformed the control group in the criteria of coherence, precision, and originality.",
    "This can be attributed to ChatGPT ability to generate structured and clear content quickly and efficiently.",
    "One of the strengths of this tool is its ability to present ideas logically, which may have facilitated the improvement of coherence in the students' projects.",
    "Additionally, by providing responses based on large volumes of information, ChatGPT is capable of offering precise data and generating novel ideas, which justifies its positive impact on the criteria of precision and originality.However, ChatGPT weaknesses also clearly emerged in the results, particularly in the criterion of source utilization, where the control group performed better.",
    "This finding suggests that, although ChatGPT can generate relevant content, it does not necessarily provide the same depth in managing academic references as traditional methods."
